
     ==========================================================
 		      Geant4 - Efficiency calibration of Germanium detector
     ==========================================================

                             README
                      ---------------------

------------------------------------------------------------------------
----> Introduction.                                                     
                                                                       
------------------------------------------------------------------------
----> 1.Experimental set-up.                                            

The direction of detector is along the z-axis, and the position of surface of detector is z=0.


-------------------------------------------------------------------------
----> 2.SET-UP 
                                          
Analysis program with ROOT is available. Energy deposit within an event will be counted into histogram. 

